{"tid":2036171,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[UC can] 我想講UC Can (聯合書院canteen) 係超級黃到冇朋友嘅餐廳","createTime":"2020-05-26T10:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T16:26:25.000Z","uid":151454,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5984e63706bc513043a7d3f754860c398379304","tid":2036171,"uid":151454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"呢間餐廳已經唔係黃可以形容到，唔係得把口支持學生，佢哋真係落手落腳去支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大保衛戰嗰時，聯合書院餐廳連續幾日準備食物給二橋前線手足，仲記得嗰時幫手跟車幫手送食物落山，連宵夜都煮埋，最後我記得佢哋係煮到冇曬食材為止，疫情關係少咗好多學生，大家得閒上嚟幫襯下，不過好似要係中大人，如果係咁，唯有等中大重新開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學地鐵站一出轉成校巴紅色B 車<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/transport_office/ABCD.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuhk.edu.hk%2Ftransport_office%2FABCD.pdf&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=3592049b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/transport_office/ABCD.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o24WkeH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo24WkeH.png&h=166ef895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPD4t6D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPD4t6D.png&h=c267b5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osH1wke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosH1wke.png&h=7877edc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合書院開心軒學生餐廳&amp;茶社<br />\nUnited College Student Canteen <br />\nMa Liu Shui<br />\n2832 2179<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/QKP5VGAW6zHcaQ7z6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FQKP5VGAW6zHcaQ7z6&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=545f7a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/QKP5VGAW6zHcaQ7z6</a><br />\n<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/joyful_inn?igsh